Name: Morri Pot
AttributesDescription: Increases ATK of all Resonators in the team by 40%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: Beef hot pots made with mushroom soup base and other ingredients. The taste is delicious, retaining the original flavor of the dish. But the selection of materials and processing must be careful, and careful again. If hallucinations occur during consumption, please seek medical attention immediately.
